q: A car travels at 22 km/h for 12 minutes. (1 km = 1000 m) What is the distance in meters?
exp: Convert speed: 22 km/h = 6.11 m/s. Time = 12 min = 720 s. Distance = speed × time = 6.11×720 ≈ 4400 m.

Step 2: 20 × 10 = 200 m.
